== counter ==
3 operations - reset, next, goto

chip that realizes this abstraction

inputs - in (16), load (1), inc (1), reset (1)
output - out (16)

if (reset[t] == 1) out[t+1] = 0
else if (load[t] == 1) out[t+1] = in[t]
else if (inc[t] == 1) out[t+1] = out[t] + 1
else out[t+1] = out[t]

default behavior - don't change value

need to write HDL
